replies.body:
@Junglerboy16, that is not why at all. Lee Sin is hated because he has been tier 1 for 4 seasons in a row. He dictates what junglers are Viable.

If a champ cannot compete with Lee Sin, you dont pick them. Thats how it has been for 4 seasons. 

Is he still king? Probably, but perhaps it is too early to tell. I honestly think his q needs to cost more energy or travel slower. Even a longer cooldown would work. Lee's only weakness is missing q, and even if he does, the window to take advantage is stupidly low.
